# Deploy ve Ortam Kontrol Kurallari

## Gizli bilgiler
- Token/key sadece `.env.local` icinde (gitignore)
- Repoya ASLA: VERCEL_TOKEN, GITHUB_TOKEN, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, anon key

## Degisiklik sonrasi kontrol
```powershell
npm run deploy:check
```

## Tam deploy (test + build + push + vercel env + check)
```powershell
npm run deploy:all
```

## Ayri komutlar
- `npm run env:check` — yerel env
- `npm run deploy:sync-vercel` — Vercel env senkron
- `.\scripts\github-push.ps1` — sadece GitHub (GITHUB_TOKEN gerekir)

## Supabase Auth redirect (production)
- `https://hesapkitap-git-main-omer-sqwqw-projects.vercel.app/auth/callback`
- Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → URL Configuration

## Vercel'de sadece su env'ler
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
- NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
- NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL (opsiyonel)
